org.asoem.greyfish.utils.collect

Class Functionals

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.asoem.greyfish.utils.collect.Functionals

  • public class Functionals
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a utility class which has the same methods as Iterables but is aware of the direct implementation in functional collections such a FunctionalCollection. That means this class decides weather to delegates to the iterables native methods or the helper methods in Iterables based on the type of the subject.
